http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/In-protest/article14617624.ece

The Telangana State Contributory Pension Scheme Employees’ Association has announced that it would observe ‘Khilafat Day’ on September 1, protesting the Contributory Pension Scheme introduced by the State government on the same day in 2004. The Association would hold a meeting at Osmania Medical College auditorium on the day at 3.30 p.m., which would be attended by representatives from employees’ and teachers’ associations.